  Ok, I'm not sure where to start but here goes...My name is Gilbane Wolfpaw, level 55 druid of Tunare.  I'm in a bind, I made the horrible mistake of fighting in Plane Of Growth, Where my God lives, Tunare.  The reason I hunted in PoG is this...I was hacked a few days before Kunark came out.  I was a level 50 with decent equipment.  The hacker destroyed all of my equipment and de-leveled me to lvl 48.  I quit EverQuest for 8 months.  When I finally returned, I was'nt sure that I was going to play, so faction and such didn't really matter to me.  Then I decided to stay...after PoG and ruining my faction.  Now I'm back better than ever, with great equipment, a great guild...but no Epic Weapon.  I cannot even start my Epic Weapon because of my faction with Tunare.  My problem is this...I have done the muffin quest with Pandos Flintside and the batwing quest in South Felwithe with the Mage Guild Leader. The factions I need are SoldersOfTunare(Druids), and FaydarksChampions(Rangers). I am KOS to both factions.  I have turned in 4,540 muffins the Pandos for both druid and ranger faction, and I have turned in 3,840 batwings to the Mage Guild Leader, this quest only offers Ranger faction.  I am still KOS to them both, thats the same as turning in 8,380 batwings if I were only after ranger faction. And I am still KOS. At least Ranger faction should have moved by now.  I have turned in all those items, 1,135 SoldersOfTunare positive faction hits, and 2,095 FaydarksChampions positive faction hits. So what I am asking is for some kind of help, every time I play EverQuest I cringe because I will never achieve my Epic Quest Weapon.  It's very frustrating, I have tryed very, very hard to achieve my faction back, and It's all in vien, for nothing, waste of time. I will never be able to walk freely in PoG again(because there is no quest to fix ServentsOfTunare faction), and I'm fine with that, I just would love to get my Epic Weapon factions back. I have spent 20+ hours working on faction quests so far.  Anyone know of anything that can help me?  This is my plead for help. Any kind of help would be great. Thanks for your time.<br>
<br>
<br>
Gilbane Wolfpaw<br>
55 Druid<br>
Tallon Zek<br>
Chosen Blood<br>
