<br>
As to your specific problem, I would recommend these steps.<br>
<br>
1.  Dying to a Faction Giver.  In the old days, this used to &quot;unsettle&quot; your faction and let it move again.  It sounds bizarre, but has worked for me once or twice.<br>
<br>
2.  Hunt in the Ocean of Tears.  Kill Pirates and hand in the Bracer of Erolissi and pirate earrings to the Leader Sister of Erolissi.  You can bind outside the pirate hut (Captain Sureshot) and then hand in the items after you egress.  This will take a long time, but has nice faction boosts and if you have been frozen in primary faction, you might be able to boost secondary factions such as Soldiers of Tunare there.  (I know they boost Faydark's Champions).<br>
<br>
3.  Petition and ask for faction reset.<br>
<br>
Good luck. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#e6ebd7><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/urhesolooshun.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Rhes Olooshun</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(7/23/01 11:37:33 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovequests.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4856.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Epic Faction(please help if you can)</span><hr size=1> You can also go into Crushbone and slaughter orcs during off hours with AoE.  Both of the factions in question are affected by this....) <p><a href="http://worldzone.net/"target="web"><img src="http://worldzone.net/themes/azyn//sig2.GIF"border="0"</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#f7f5e6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ugilbanewolfpaw.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Gilbane Wolfpaw</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(7/23/01 8:22:44 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovequests.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4856.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Epic Faction(please help if you can)</span><hr size=1> Thanks for the info Quaras, ill try sister isle quest and dieing to a mob on that faction<br>
